Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:37.57,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,确认前方航线上有积雨云
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.91,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,Neopan400 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.54,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,积雨云的气压状况没有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.16,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,保持航线，按预定时间到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.25,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,Ekta64 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那个…明日香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}已经先出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看来她彻底不想看到我的脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣你还不了解女人心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那个…     对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}请说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}四号机空号的传闻是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}听说发生某种事故爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯，是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}四号机跟 NERV 第 2 支部一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在 S  引擎的试验过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\pos(241,435)\fs18}2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这里没问题的，3 台不都运行得很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}而且驾驶员和工作人员都很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}但听说从美国运来的三号机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}要在松代做启动试验，对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯…虽然我得在外地待上四天左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不过加持会来照料的，放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可是试验…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}律子也会一起参加，不会有问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可是驾驶员…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}关于…那个驾驶员…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在下，今天有事来拜托葛城少校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}请让我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}让我当 EVANGELION 三号机的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这么说真嗣还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一直没有机会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}有时候实在不知道他在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不是你自己主动要当监护人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}话是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那，什么时候叫驾驶员过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}明天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还有很多东西要准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}他说不定会自己说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我想不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}他并没有高兴到会去跟别人炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}将住院中的妹妹转院到总部的医学部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这是他提出的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}美里小姐好冷淡啊，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}要说干劲的话我绝对排第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}就算是候补也好啊，只要肯用我就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吧？冬二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}明明先出门却这么晚才到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今天你们夫妻不吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我只是不想看到你们的脸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你们这个笨蛋三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那就…吃饭喽、吃饭喽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}奇怪？冬二人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那家伙会连饭都不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}他这阵子怪怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}铃原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}原来是绫波啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}要找真嗣的话，他不在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你知道我的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\fs30\fnEVA-FANS方正粗宋v3}惣{\r}流好像也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不知道的只有真嗣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}难得你会担心别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你担心的人是真嗣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}小光～～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}{\pos(385,448)\c&Hff00ff&}{\fs30\fnMS Mincho}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一起吃便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}迟到 2 个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}现在终于给我出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}第一次有男人让我等这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}要是约会你根本不等就马上回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}…以上所述
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}就是这世上所说的第二次冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我当时住在根府川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不过，南极大陆融化导致水位上升
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}使得那边现在变成海底了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}抱歉了，转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}老子非揍你一拳不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不揍你我没办法消气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}对不起，明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}平时你都是跟碇君一起回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}没关系啦，跟真嗣在一起只是义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}而且今天我不想看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是关于铃原的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯…你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}再明显不过了，大概只有那笨蛋三人组还不解风情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可是碇同学虽然比较单纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那家伙最迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}而且又笨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}根本不知道怎么跟别人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}铃原喜欢的女孩…说不定是绫波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}铃原?! 喜欢那个优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}中午…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看起来感情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}放心啦小光，那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}说到人际交往，那个女的比真嗣还差一万倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可以问你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那个热血笨蛋好在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}他的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:35.61,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：啊～当初跟你和好果然是个天大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:36.75,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 男：到现在了才这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.66,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：不，现在还不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:41.04,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：确实，人生布满了陷阱。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.86,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：但是就算掉进去了，只要再爬出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.81,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 男：我就是所谓的陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.53,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：啊～也没有那么悲观啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:50.52,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：绝望的尽头必然会有希望的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.90,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 男：那我是绝望的代名词？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.60,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：没错，你一定是为了跟我分手才接近我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.32,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 男：我哪有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.43,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：大概也没有什么女人会在接不好吻的男人身上浪费时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.73,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a3}[TV] 男：接不好吻……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.26,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 女：没错，而且不止是不会接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:02.98,BGS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a1}[TV] 男：不止不会接吻……
