Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}葛城不在就这样吗
